# Simple Pyramid with Normals
o Pyramid

# Vertices
v  0  1  0    # Top vertex
v -1  0 -1    # Bottom-left front
v  1  0 -1    # Bottom-right front
v  1  0  1    # Bottom-right back
v -1  0  1    # Bottom-left back

# Normals
vn  0  1  0   # Upwards (top vertex normal)
vn  0 -1  0   # Downwards (base normal)
vn -1  1 -1   # Slope left-front
vn  1  1 -1   # Slope right-front
vn  1  1  1   # Slope right-back
vn -1  1  1   # Slope left-back

# Faces
f 1//3 2//3 3//3   # Front triangle
f 1//4 3//4 4//4   # Right triangle
f 1//5 4//5 5//5   # Back triangle
f 1//6 5//6 2//6   # Left triangle

f 2//2 3//2 4//2   # Base (front-right)
f 2//2 4//2 5//2   # Base (left-back)
